{"type":null,"faqId":40445,"title":"Wi-Fi经常掉线，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>建议将路由器远离微波炉等信号强干扰源。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>如果 Wi-Fi 信号比较弱，可以尝试调整一下路由器的位置。选择开阔空间，减少路由器和上网设备之间的阻挡物，例如水泥墙、木板墙等阻挡物会影响Wi-Fi信号传输效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>如果Wi-Fi信号强但速率较低，可以尝试连接到路由器的5G Wi-Fi，5G干扰较少。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>如果房子太大导致有些地方 Wi-Fi 信号弱，可以尝试将路由器与智联配件无线扩展器WS331c或PT500+PT530搭配使用，实现整套房子的 Wi-Fi 全覆盖。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>如果搜索附近有多个 Wi-Fi，建议将路由器的Wi-Fi信道设置为“</span><span class=\"s2\">自适应</span><span>”，避免与附近的多个Wi-Fi信号在同一信道，从而减少Wi-Fi干扰。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>登录路由器Web配置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">2  </span><span>单击“</span><span class=\"s2\">更多功能 &gt; Wi-Fi 设置 &gt; Wi-Fi 高级</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">3  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">2.4G Wi-Fi 信道</span><span>”和“</span><span class=\"s2\">5G Wi-Fi 信道</span><span>”中更换信道。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137276\" style=\"width:5.5111113in;height:6.365278in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5792","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768489000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":74,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}